            <p class='font-bold italic text-center'>Nous contacter :</p>
            <div class='flex flex-col items-center gap-4 justify-center mt-4'>
                <p>
                    Via le formulaire de <a
                        href='/contact'
                        class='underline underline-offset-4 decoration-red-500'
                        >contact</a>
                </p>
                <p class='flex gap-2'>
                    Par mail:
                    <a href={`mailto:${emailAddress}`} class='cursor-pointer'>
